file.name: parameters-array.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.2"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://example.com
tags:
  - name: search
    description: Search
paths:
  /default-style:
    get:
      summary: Get some info
      operationId: info
      parameters:
        - name: strings
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: array
            maxItems: 4
            items:
              type: string
        - name: integers
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: array
            maxItems: 4
            items:
              type: integer
        - name: nested[integers]
          in: query
          required: false
          explode: false
          schema:
            type: array
            maxItems: 4
            items:
              type: integer
      responses:
        "200":
          description: ok
